WEBVTT

32:46.090 --> 32:50.990 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

32:46.230 --> 32:47.940 line:80%
May your spirit in heaven

32:48.380 --> 32:51.240 line:80%
bless the people of Great Yin
with peace and safety.

32:51.630 --> 32:53.750 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

32:52.740 --> 32:54.400 line:80%
If you happen to meet my parents,

32:54.340 --> 32:57.050 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪
